OL,3,CBritish mother who abducted sons from
OL,4,CUS father has been on run in UK for
OL,5,Cmonths
OL,7,FA British mother who abducted her two
OL,8,Fsons from their American father has
OL,9,Fbeen on the run in the UK for over
OL,10,Fthree months, it can be reported.
OL,12,FNishika Samaratunga, a 34-year-old
OL,13,FBritish citizen originally from Sri
OL,14,FLanka, is believed to be concealing
OL,15,Fthe whereabouts of her two children,
OL,16,Ffive-year-old Blaine Baier and three-
OL,17,Fyear-old Nathaniel Baier, known as
OL,18,FNate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784168292
OL,3,CBritish mother who abducted sons from
OL,4,CUS father has been on run in UK for
OL,5,Cmonths
OL,7,FThe boys were born in the United
OL,8,FStates and were being cared for by
OL,9,Ftheir father, Ben Baier, who lives
OL,10,Fnear Denver, Colorado.
OL,12,FBlaine and Nathaniel visited their
OL,13,Fmother in the UK in March as part of
OL,14,Fcourt-ordered contact following their
OL,15,Fparents' divorce but Ms Samaratunga
OL,16,Ffailed to return them to Mr Baier at a
OL,17,FUK airport on March 29, and she and
OL,18,Fthe boys have not been located since.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784168292
OL,3,CBritish mother who abducted sons from
OL,4,CUS father has been on run in UK for
OL,5,Cmonths
OL,7,FMr Baier, 43, has begun High Court
OL,8,Fproceedings to try to secure his sons'
OL,9,Freturn, with his lawyers raising
OL,10,Fconcerns that the two boys do not
OL,11,Fappear to be attending school or
OL,12,Fnursery and are not receiving medical
OL,13,Fcare.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784168292
OL,3,CBritish mother who abducted sons from
OL,4,CUS father has been on run in UK for
OL,5,Cmonths
OL,7,FMr Baier said: "The collapse of my
OL,8,Fmarriage has been an incredibly trying
OL,9,Ftime, but I never believed that
OL,10,FNishika would abduct Blaine and
OL,11,FNathaniel and then conceal their
OL,12,Fwhereabouts in an effort to keep them
OL,13,Ffrom me, uprooting them from their
OL,14,Fhome in Colorado.
OL,16,F"Both our children have autism, and
OL,17,Fsuch abrupt changes to their routine
OL,18,Fare incredibly damaging to their
OL,19,Fdevelopment and health.
OL,26,@oD@POUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784168292
OL,3,CBritish mother who abducted sons from
OL,4,CUS father has been on run in UK for
OL,5,Cmonths
OL,7,F"I'm calling for her to do the right
OL,8,Fthing and return them to me so they
OL,9,Fcan return to their life as normal,
OL,10,Fand for anyone who knows where they
OL,11,Fare to help return them to their home.
OL,13,F"I can only pray for their safe
OL,14,Freturn."
OL,16,FThe High Court has allowed the
OL,17,Fpublication of details of the case to
OL,18,Fhelp locate the children.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
