CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784168292
OL,3,CBritish mother who abducted sons from
OL,4,CUS father has been on run in UK for
OL,5,Cmonths
OL,7,FMr Baier and Ms Samaratunga married in
OL,8,F2020, with Ms Samaratunga moving to
OL,9,Fthe US, but their relationship broke
OL,10,Fdown in 2024.
OL,12,FMs Samaratunga then applied to a
OL,13,FColorado court to relocate the
OL,14,Fchildren to London in August last year
OL,15,Fbut returned to the UK the following
OL,16,Fmonth after this was refused.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784168292
OL,3,CBritish mother who abducted sons from
OL,4,CUS father has been on run in UK for
OL,5,Cmonths
OL,7,FShe made further requests to relocate
OL,8,Fthe children but a Colorado court
OL,9,Fordered in October that Mr Baier
OL,10,Fbecome their sons' primary custodial
OL,11,Fparent.
OL,13,FWhile the Colorado court ordered that
OL,14,Fthe children must remain in the state,
OL,15,Fit also ordered Mr Baier to take the
OL,16,Fchildren to England so they could
OL,17,Fspend time with Ms Samaratunga, with a
OL,18,Ffirst visit taking place between
OL,19,FDecember and January.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784168292
OL,3,CBritish mother who abducted sons from
OL,4,CUS father has been on run in UK for
OL,5,Cmonths
OL,7,FBut when Mr Baier went to the airport
OL,8,Fto take his sons back to the US
OL,9,Ffollowing the second visit in March,
OL,10,FMs Samaratunga failed to return them,
OL,11,Fin breach of the order of the Colorado
OL,12,Fcourt.
OL,14,FThe High Court in London has since
OL,15,Fissued orders against several
OL,16,Fcompanies to trace Ms Samaratunga,
OL,17,Fincluding JP Morgan Chase, HSBC,
OL,18,FThames Water and the NHS, but no
OL,19,Finformation has become available as to
OL,20,Fher whereabouts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784168292
OL,3,CBritish mother who abducted sons from
OL,4,CUS father has been on run in UK for
OL,5,Cmonths
OL,7,FA judge in Colorado also authorised
OL,8,FAmerican law enforcement to take
OL,9,Fcustody of the children in April,
OL,10,Fciting a "credible risk that the
OL,11,Fchildren are in imminent danger".
OL,13,FThey added that Ms Samaratunga had
OL,14,F"engaged in activities indicating a
OL,15,Fplanned abduction" and had
OL,16,F"unilaterally prevented the children's
OL,17,Fcourt-ordered return".
OL,19,FThis meant the children were
OL,20,F"presently physically and emotionally
OL,21,Fendangered".
OL,26,@rD@JOUsD@`O]vD@AOUwD@RO]xD@AOUyD@UO]|D@
OL,26,AAOU}D@KO]
