OL,3,CBritish mother who abducted sons from
OL,4,CUS father has been on run in UK for
OL,5,Cmonths
OL,7,FAmy Rowe, partner at Hunters Law LLP,
OL,8,Frepresenting Mr Baier, said: "The
OL,9,Fcourt has rightly recognised the
OL,10,Fdeeply harmful impact of abduction on
OL,11,FBlaine and Nathaniel.
OL,13,F"These are two very young, vulnerable
OL,14,Fchildren and every day that they
OL,15,Fremain missing increases the concern
OL,16,Ffor their welfare.
OL,18,F"It is imperative that they are found
OL,19,Fand returned home safely as soon as
OL,20,Fpossible."
OL,26,@pD@^OUuD@AOUzD@AOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
